19:25.365 --> 19:27.334
Hey,
what's going on with you?

19:27.400 --> 19:28.501
Nothing.

19:28.568 --> 19:30.270
Good movie.
Glad I picked it.

19:32.839 --> 19:34.807
Dog's having
