the dog is dying,

19:38.945 --> 19:41.381
and the kitten
just went over a waterfall.

19:41.448 --> 19:42.682
Nothing?

19:42.749 --> 19:46.686
Your Uncle Kyle
told me your little plan.

19:46.753 --> 19:50.457
Apparently, you want
an emotionless dreamboat.

19:50.523 --> 19:53.660
Well...you got him.

19:59.332 --> 20:01.734
Okay, Chale, look,
I made a huge mistake.

20:01.801 --> 20:03.636
I-I shouldn't have tried
to change you.

20:03.703 --> 20:07.039
Just be who you are,
because...I love that person.

20:07.106 --> 20:08.375
Really?

20:08.441 --> 20:10.009
Yeah.

20:10.076 --> 20:11.278
Okay, good.

20:11.344 --> 20:13.880
Because when the kitten
went over the waterfall,

20:13.946 --> 20:15.815
(Sobbing)
he had his little...

20:17.317 --> 20:19.719
It was just --
it was too much.

20:19.786 --> 20:21.521
You okay (Sobs) with this?

20:22.789 --> 20:23.923
More or less.

20:23.990 --> 20:26.058
Oh, thank you.

20:26.125 --> 20:28.060
( Sobbing )

20:28.127 --> 20:29.462
Oh.

20:29.529 --> 20:31.398
I'm sorry
it didn't work out, Chale.

20:34.200 --> 20:35.268
If it's any consolation,

20:35.335 --> 20:38.271
I'll pay for your flight
back to England.

20:38.338 --> 20:39.872
Dad,
we're not breaking up.

20:39.939 --> 20:41.574
Offer still stands.

